{
  "texts": [
    "We focus on tuning language models belonging into two categories.",
    "First, we fine-tune variations of encoder models, namely BERT (Devlin et al., 2019), RoBERTa-large (Liu et al., 2019) and DeBERTaV3base (He et al., 2023), to assess the impact of transfer learning using various datasets requiring similar reasoning abilities, apart from BrainTeaser.",
    "We study the problem using the provided multichoice setup, but we also transform it into a binary classification task.",
    "Secondly, the encoders' results are compared with those obtained from finetuned LLMs using the BrainTeaser dataset.",
    "To achieve this, we fine-tune Llama 2 (Touvron et al., 2023b), Phi-2 (Gunasekar et al., 2023) and Mistral-7b (Jiang et al., 2024a), which have already demonstrated enhanced reasoning abilities."
  ]
}